  "How many cards are in Slay the Spire 2?": { eng: "How many cards are in Slay the Spire 2?", deu: "Wie viele Karten gibt es in Slay the Spire 2?", esp: "¿Cuántas cartas hay en Slay the Spire 2?", fra: "Combien de cartes y a-t-il dans Slay the Spire 2 ?", ita: "Quante carte ci sono in Slay the Spire 2?", jpn: "Slay the Spire 2にはカードが何枚ありますか？", kor: "Slay the Spire 2에는 카드가 몇 장 있나요?", pol: "Ile kart jest w Slay the Spire 2?", ptb: "Quantas cartas há em Slay the Spire 2?", rus: "Сколько карт в Slay the Spire 2?", spa: "¿Cuántas cartas hay en Slay the Spire 2?", tha: "ใน Slay the Spire 2 มีการ์ดกี่ใบ?", tur: "Slay the Spire 2'de kaç kart var?", zhs: "Slay the Spire 2 中有多少张卡牌?" },
